overview: NOAH: Great Voyage 2023 in Yokohama was a professional wrestling event promoted by CyberFight's sub-brand Pro Wrestling Noah. It took place on March 19, 2023, in Yokohama, Japan, at the Yokohama Budokan. NOAH returns to Yokohama in their first big event post Keiji Muto’s retirement, and this show could dictate the rest of the year for NOAH. Great Voyage 2023 has three huge title matches, and lots of stuff to look forward to on the undercard.
title: NOAH: Great Voyage 2023 in Yokohama
